summary: A Comprehensive checklist of all items in Vanilla Skyrim (not including junk items) for the ultimate collector of all the things
descriptionHtml:
[u][b]Update Log
[/b][/u]version 2.0:

A Letter from a Friend
Lakeview Manor Charter
Windstad Manor Charter
Heljarchen Hall Charter

Vampire faction
Thalmor faction

Added Misc. Items:

A complete checklist of every (Non junk, non-crafting material) item, if there is a demand i will create a junk item checklist or a crafting item checklist, potentially both, i spent a lot of time putting this list together and making it look good, please if you see any mistakes, alert me so that i can fix them. All pictures that are found in the file were obtained from http://www.uesp.net/wiki/Skyrim:Skyrim
author: Evilisme23
